nodes.text: Star Wars: Han Solo - Imperial Cadet

Star Wars: Han Solo - Imperial Cadet is a Marvel Comics miniseries. The series is by Robbie Thompson with art by Leonard Kirk, and released its first issue on November 7, 2018. The limited comic series focuses on Han Solo just after joining the Imperial Military, concurrently to Solo: A Star Wars Story.
